Class RegisteredThread

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • com.github.aklakina.edmma.logicalUnit.threading.RegisteredThread
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    public class RegisteredThread
extends java.lang.Thread
    Class representing a registered thread. This thread is registered to a singleton factory and has a closer method.
